Package: hts
Title: Interactive Shiny Workflow for WorldClim Raster Processing
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Mariana", "Castaneda Guzman", email = "mcguzman1997@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    Provides an interactive Shiny application that demonstrates a reproducible
    geospatial workflow using WorldClim bioclimatic data. The app downloads
    global climate rasters, extracts BIO1 (Annual Mean Temperature), crops and
    masks the raster to South America using a local shapefile, and visualizes
    each processing step.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
